									<p><strong>Syiah Kuala Law Journal</strong> is a legal periodical, managed and published by Master of Laws Study Program, Faculty of Law, Syiah Kuala University. First edition of the journal was published in 2017 as a replacement of <a title="Jurnal Ilmu Hukum" href="https://jurnal.usk.ac.id/MIH/issue/archive" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong><em>Jurnal Ilmu Hukum</em></strong></a>, a law journal previously managed by Post-Graduate Study Program of Syiah Kuala University.</p>
