								<a href="https://publications.usk.ac.id/index.php/JTS" rel="bookmark">
									Jurnal Teknik Sipil
								</a>
							</h3>
															<div class="description">
									<p>Jurnal Teknik Sipil (Journal of Civil Engineering) is a scientific journal, published by Civil Engineering Department, Faculty of Engineering, Universitas Syiah Kuala. It is aimed at disseminating research results related to civil engineering fields, where readers of the journal are expected from civil engineering researchers/scientists, students in related fields, engineers, and practitioners in this field.</p>
<p>Jurnal Teknik Sipil (Journal of Civil Engineering) has been established since 2011, with the first edition Volume 1, Number 1, September 2011. Since then, it has published 13 Volumes and 1 Special Issue Volume.</p>
<p>Started in May 2018, the publication period of the journal has been changed to two times in a year, i.e. in May and in November. It was started by Volume 7 No. 1, in 2018. This is to allow a more rigor process of publications and to allow editorial boards to refine the performance of the journal.</p>
<p>Jurnal Teknik Sipil (Journal of Civil Engineering) Universitas Syiah Kuala publishes the scientific articles in area of civil engineering, as follows:<br />-Structural Engineering,<br />-Water Resources Engineering,<br />-Transportation Engineering,<br />-Geotechnical Engineering, <br />-Construction Engineering &amp; Management, <br />-Urban Planning<br />-Geospatial and Geomatic Engineering, and Ocean Engineering</p>
<p>All the submitted papers will undergo a blind-review process, from at least two anonymous reviewers. In general, Jurnal Teknil Sipil put high priorities to papers that can demonstrate its originality, novelty, and significant findings that can be useful for interest readers. A similarity check for all submitted papers will be applied to ensure the quality of the paper. Above all, editorial boards of Jurnal Teknik Sipil are committed to allow quality papers to contribute to the field of civil engineering.</p>
<p>On behalf of Editorial Board of Jurnal Teknik Sipil, we hereby invite you to publish your manuscript to Jurnal Teknik Sipil. Simultaneously, we sincerely offer our gratitude to reviewers from various universities/institutions who have been voluntarily reviewing the submitted articles. Your valuable input have shaped our scientific contribution in this field.</p>
<p>Thank you very much.</p>
<p>Regards,</p>
<p>Prof. Syamsidik (Editor in Chief of Jurnal Teknik Sipil Universitas Syiah Kuala)</p>
